<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='304000' id='t-304000'>that had been confiscated.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='306000' id='t-306000'>All the peoples that the Babylonians had repressed and removed</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='309000' id='t-309000'>will go home,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='311000' id='t-311000'>and they'll take with them their gods.</span>
