<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='317000' id='t-317000'>and to worship their gods</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='319000' id='t-319000'>in their own way, in their own place.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='322000' id='t-322000'>This is the decree,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='324000' id='t-324000'>this object is the evidence</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='327000' id='t-327000'>for the fact that the Jews,</span>
