<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='340000' id='t-340000'>They were allowed to return to Jerusalem</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='342000' id='t-342000'>and to rebuild the temple.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='344000' id='t-344000'>It's a central document</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='346000' id='t-346000'>in Jewish history.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='348000' id='t-348000'>And the Book of Chronicles, the Book of Ezra in the Hebrew scriptures</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='352000' id='t-352000'>reported in ringing terms.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='354000' id='t-354000'>This is the Jewish version</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='356000' id='t-356000'>of the same story.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='358000' id='t-358000'>&quot;Thus said Cyrus, king of Persia,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='360000' id='t-360000'>'All the kingdoms of the earth have the Lord God of heaven given thee,</span>
