<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='365000' id='t-365000'>to build him a house in Jerusalem.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='367000' id='t-367000'>Who is there among you of his people?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='369000' id='t-369000'>The Lord God be with him,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='371000' id='t-371000'>and let him go up.'&quot;</span>
