<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='405000' id='t-405000'>Two great texts,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='407000' id='t-407000'>what about the politics?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='409000' id='t-409000'>What was going on</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='411000' id='t-411000'>was the fundamental shift in Middle Eastern history.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='414000' id='t-414000'>The empire of Iran, the Medes and the Persians,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='417000' id='t-417000'>united under Cyrus,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419000' id='t-419000'>became the first great world empire.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='423000' id='t-423000'>Cyrus begins in the 530s BC.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='426000' id='t-426000'>And by the time of his son Darius,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='430000' id='t-430000'>the whole of the eastern Mediterranean</span>
