<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467000' id='t-467000'>Cyrus sets up a model</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='469000' id='t-469000'>of how you run</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='471000' id='t-471000'>a great multinational, multifaith, multicultural society.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476000' id='t-476000'>And the result of that</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='478000' id='t-478000'>was an empire that included the areas you see on the screen,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='481000' id='t-481000'>and which survived for 200 years of stability</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='484000' id='t-484000'>until it was shattered by Alexander.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='487000' id='t-487000'>It left a dream of the Middle East as a unit,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='489000' id='t-489000'>and a unit where people of different faiths</span>
