<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='548000' id='t-548000'>Meanwhile, back in Babylon,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='550000' id='t-550000'>things had not been going well.</span>
