11:49
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698000' id='t-698000'>God, we know,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='700000' id='t-700000'>is usually on the side of the big battalions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702000' id='t-702000'>The question is, which god was it?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='705000' id='t-705000'>And the debate unsettles</span>
