<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='725000' id='t-725000'>And there's a slight sense that Isaiah knows this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='728000' id='t-728000'>because he says,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='730000' id='t-730000'>this is God speaking, of course,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733000' id='t-733000'>&quot;I have called thee by thy name</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='735000' id='t-735000'>though thou hast not known me.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='737000' id='t-737000'>I think it's recognized</span>
